Name: Super Blackout
About the game: Can you 'black out' all of the lit-up tiles in this addictive puzzle game? Super Blackout packs a lot of value for its low price, complete with 90 puzzles, an endless random puzzle generator, and even the ability to design your own puzzles! Playable with either controller, mouse, or keyboard.
